*** What is Feature file? Why is it used?
Feature file follows BDD approach (Behavior Driven Development) so that anyone in a team from technical/non-technical background can easily understand the test scenarios. (Business Team, DEV and Testing team)
It provides clear communication for all stakeholders.
It helps to maintain up-to-date documentation.
It helps to understand the expected behavior of the system.

We use Gherkin keywords such as Given, When, Then to write the scenarios.





